XTCTrajectory is a simple pDynamo module for reading and 
writing trajectory files in the compressed XTC format of Gromacs.

For installation instructions, see the file INSTALL.

For questions and comments, contact: mikolaj.feliks@gmail.com

The module is distributed under the CeCILL Free Software License, which is
a French equivalent of the GNU General Public License. For details, see the
files: Licence_CeCILL_V2-en.txt and Licence_CeCILL_V2-fr.txt.

Resources:
- xdrfile library
http://www.gromacs.org/Developer_Zone/Programming_Guide/XTC_Library

- pDynamo
http://pdynamo.org
